# Web UI build
web/dist/
web/node_modules/

# npm lockfile — web/ uses pnpm, never npm. Dependabot scans any
# package-lock.json it finds, so an accidental `npm install` would
# recreate a stale lockfile and reopen already-fixed alerts. Tier 96.
